Package net.enilink.composition.asm

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BehaviourClassProcessor
    Implements or transforms BehaviourClassNodes.
    BehaviourMethodProcessor
    Implements or transforms methods of a BehaviourClassNode.
    CompositeClassProcessor
    Interface for processors that implement a transformation of a CompositeClassNode.
    Types
    Common type definitions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AsmUtils
    Utility methods for the transformation process.
    BehaviourClassNode
    Represents the mutable structure of a behaviour class.
    BehaviourFactoryBase
    Abstract implementation for BehaviourFactorys that use BehaviourClassProcessors and BehaviourMethodProcessors to create concrete behaviour classes.
    Checks
    Utility methods for general assertions.
    CompositeClassNode
    Represents the mutable structure of a composite class.
    DefaultBehaviourFactory
    The default factory that is used to transform abstract behaviours into concrete behaviours.
    ExtendedClassNode
    Represents the mutable structure of a Java class.
    ExtendedMethod
    Represents a mutable method that knows its owner class.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    DependsOn
    Annotation for BehaviourMethodProcessors to express a dependency to other processors.
    UseWith
    Annotation for BehaviourClassProcessors and BehaviourMethodProcessors to restrict the BehaviourFactorys that are allowed use them.
